text: Fantastic opportunity for an exceptional, ready to build, fully serviced lot in the highly desired Lynden School District. Located on the East Side of Lynden amongst the most beautiful, wide-open spaces.

Bellingham Bay View Home w/ remodeled Main floor, updated bsmt. Upper Kitchen is High-end. Lower Kitchen is original. ADU/rental poss downstairs. Lot runs to Morey Ave- new regs may allow added rental units. Once inside, youll be drawn to the full width Bay view. On the large deck you have an ever-changing seascape. Coming back inside, notice all the varnished natural woodwork & solid wood floors. The custom Kitchen is a cooks delight w/ Viking Range & SS appliances. Down the hall is a bath w lg tile shower, Bedroom, & Main Suite w/ walk-in closet, tub/toilet/tiled-shower/& double sinks. Downstairs: Family Room, Office/Br, ba, laundry, & Kitchen-Dining Room. Extra bsmt sq ft (shop) to convert to large 2nd Ensuite bed/bath.

Opportunity knocks for anyone looking for a prime South Hill, unobstructed view - no powerlines, location to build or rehab a home. Bring your creativity to this turn of the century home or start new. Either way you'll enjoy 180 degree panoramic views - you must see it to believe it! Crystal clear blue skies and endless sunsets at your fingertips on a street lined with gorgeous homes. How rare to have such a clear view of the bay, islands, mountains, and city lights with views toward Fairhaven and Bellingham Harbor! The home offers a great base for your new project including a detached garage w/ alley access. New laws may present future opportunity for multiple dwellings - attached or detached. Don't let this one pass you by!

Meticulously maintained home nestled on a serene tiered lot backing onto a tranquil pond and greenspace. The spacious floor plan boasts a large kitchen, living room & great room, perfect for unforgettable gatherings. Featuring 9-foot ceilings, a luxurious primary bedroom with ensuite bath & walk-in closet, shaker-style maple cabinets, granite-tile counters, hardwood oak floors, large kitchen island & laundry room with additional utility sink and ample storage. Recent upgrades include a new roof (2021) and a new furnace and central A/C (2022). The sunlit SW-facing deck & generously sized yard are ideal for both relaxation and lively entertainment. Conveniently located near charming downtown Ferndale and walking distance to multiple schools.

Modern, cozy, rustic A-Frame on a dead end street, ample space for outdoor living on this large corner lot. House has been fully updated with brand new septic tank, new metal roof, fully updated electrical including 50 amp RV hook up/EV charger. Interior features LVP flooring throughout, new kitchen with butcher block counters and all new appliances. Cozy bathroom with tiled corner shower and lower spout perfect for washing feet or furry friends. Never worry about running out of hot water with the new tankless water heater. $20, 000 of previously approved plans for an attached garage and second story addition to convey with house. Footings already inspected and poured. Come make this beautiful house home.

Birch Bay Village prime building lot. Rare no issues level, large, ideally located site. 25% larger than average-sized lot in the community at 12, 000 + sq. ft. Only a block from entry gate & 1 of the few remaining undeveloped lots on Comox Ridge. Ideal for custom or spec home. Peace of mind 24/7 manned guard gated security. Birch Bay Village residents enjoy access to newly completed private marina, tennis, pickleball, clubhouse, pool, beach access, golf & more. Located in the Pacific NW's famous Rain Shadow with only 27 avg. rainfall per year. 15 minutes to U.S./ Canada Border and under 30 minutes to Bellingham. Come Home to a Vacation, Come Home to Birch Bay Village . Build your dream home today or hold as a prudent investment.

Here is a wonderful opportunity to develop this property in the Puget neighborhood into building lots. The City of Bellingham advised that the 15 lots need to have 2 combined into 1 and have new lot line adjustments. Water is run down the road, electricity, and gas are to the corner. Still needs a road, sewer, and storm drain. Buyers are to check with COB to verify all information.

Beautifully updated 2 bedroom condo in the Raspberry Ridge 55+ Community. This single level, duplex style condo features a spacious single level layout. The tastefully updated kitchen is complete with Kitchen Aid appliances, large pantry, and island with prep sink. Primary bedroom with bath and walk-in closet. Many upgrades throughout, including wood floors, Hunter Douglas blinds, ceiling fans and central A/C. Beautiful, low maintenance outdoor space with private patio overlooking Raspberry Ridge Golf Course. Attached garage includes utility sink, large workbench, and storage space. Centrally located between Bellingham and Lynden allows for easy access to shopping and services.

The perfect single-story home in Lynden, just like new! A 2022 build with vaulted ceilings and a bright, welcoming great room. Stainless steel appliances, beautiful matching granite countertops throughout, modern hardware and finishes, gas stove, 3 beds | 2 bathrooms, a nice-sized laundry room and private, fenced yard for your furry friends. This move-in ready home is waiting for you! Come live the Lynden dream in this established neighborhood.

Welcome to Northview, where contemporary solar living meets stunning mountain and golf course views. Elevate your lifestyle with this better than new, model home proudly featured in Bellingham Alive. Open concept layout blends functionality and elegance. Modern kitchen boasts high end finishes, an over-sized island and a walk-in pantry with additional flex space. Mini-split heat pump ensures comfort, while solar panels maximize savings, epitomizing eco-friendly living. Wired for electric car charging. Large, fully fenced yard offers private retreat overlooking the golf course. Enjoy nearby amenities like brand new regional Cordata park, scenic bike lanes, trails, & shopping. Easy access to I-5 puts Seattle & Vancouver city life within reach.

Check out this nearly new, modern home in the Mt Baker Rim community. Whether a full time residence or vacation home, this almost 1, 600 sqft home features a gorgeous kitchen with stainless appliances and quartz counters, perfect for entertaining large groups. Situated on a very nice flat and sunny lot with all the modern features you might need including a metal roof, generator, gorgeous firepit area, A/C and much more! Trimmed out with cedar accents on the outside, planked vaulted ceilings inside and a bright open floorplan, this home lives large with a bedroom, gear room, and office/den on the main floor and a loft sitting area along with another large bedroom on the second floor. With 2 bathrooms including laundry, this home has it all!

Discover the promising potential of this 3bed 2bth home in the quiet community of South Bay. Spacious 1906sqft of living space, this home presents an opportunity for updating to add your personal touch. Sitting on a large 5 acres with towering evergreens & ample outdoor space perfect for gardening, entertaining & enjoying peace & quiet. The highlight is its access to lakefront leisure with deeded shared Lake Whatcom waterfront, for countless days of adventures & relaxation. Beyond the homes privacy and tranquil setting there is a large shop that presents an excellent storage for all your toys! This is an amazing opportunity for creating your dream home while embracing a peaceful lifestyle where natural beauty meets limitless potential.

This condo is a prime location walkable to WWU, downtown Bellingham, Co-op and farmers market. Easy access to trails, waterfront parks, & Fairhaven.Covered assigned parking space, on-site laundry facilities, & secure 6x6 storage on-site.The living room double bed unit with built-in desk, & shelving stays.The condo has an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, butcher block counters, & renovated bathroom.Radiant heat & closet organizers enhance the convenience and practicality of this condo.There are breathtaking views of the water, cityscape, & sunsets from the large covered balcony.Ramp access from High Street adds to the accessibility and convenience of entering the unit, making it ideal for individuals with mobility considerations.

Welcome to the Gardiner Terrace Community! This 3 bed, 2 full bath single level home has flowing open floor plan. Kitchen has been fully updated and has newer stainless steel appliances. Formal dining room, eating space off kitchen, breakfast bar and family room make this home perfect for entertaining. Primary bedroom has en suite bath with soaking tub, shower and spacious walk-in closet. Radiant heat throughout with new high-end/tech boiler. Utility room with nice washer/dryer set leads to huge 3 car garage with workspace for all of your projects and toys! Located on a fully fenced, well-kept, 12, 197 sqft lot. Close to schools, parks, shopping, amenities, restaurants and less than 20 minutes to Bellingham!

Mid-county gem in Lynden Schools! 2 homes + shop on 2.85 acres boast stunning views of Mt. Baker and Twin Sisters. Set back off the road in private park-like setting, the main house, 2500 sq ft, features mid-century charm with a daylight basement and split-level formal living and dining with vaulted ceilings, open beams, rock wall, gas FP, and huge picture windows that take in the view. 4 bd, 2.5 ba, formal and informal space, primary bd with 3/4 bath, family room w/ gas FP and attached XL 2-car garage/workroom. Second home, 1030 sq ft, single-story with 3 bd, 2 ba, offers privacy with a separate drive. A 36'x60' insulated/heated shop with crane and offices complete the package. Mature cedars, fenced yards, circular driveways and more!

This charming, fully remodeled 2-bedroom, 1-bath condo is a true gem. No stairs! Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior, featuring a cozy living space and a tastefully designed kitchen with modern appliances and delightful finishes. The bright and airy bedrooms offer comfort and tranquility, while the sleek bathroom exudes style and functionality. Nestled in a desirable location, this home provides easy access to local amenities, parks, and schools. Includes two assigned parking spots. A cozy back patio with a custom cover keeps you dry in any weather. Don't miss out on the cutest kitchen in townschedule your viewing today!

This is it, city living with a country feel! You'll find yourself just minutes away from schools, parks, groceries, dining, and all the other necessary conveniences! The property is NOT in a flood zone, and the City of Nooksack makes permitting a breeze. Come bring your plans and start building your dream today!

Welcome to condo living on the Raspberry Ridge GC. This lovely condo looks out toward the 5th hole and offers views of the course and mountains. Single level home that feels less like a condo with a large 2 car garage & private driveway. Step inside to an open & spacious main living space blending with the kitchen and dining. Brand new laminate flooring adds a contemporary touch & easy to maintain. Two bedrooms including a primary suite with walk in closet & private bathroom. Small flex area off laundry room. The back patio offers a gas hookup for your barbecue. Raspberry Ridge is a sought after 55+ community with easy access to Bellingham and Lynden while offering access to a quick round of golf or enjoying the game from your patio.

Home and condominium buyers, this is a recently remodeled South Hill, 3-bedroom, 1.75 bath, bay view home, which comes with a low maintenance yard and is located near the heart of Fairhaven. The home was remodeled by Moceri Construction in 2018, with additional improvements by Ethos West. As the yard requires little maintenance, it is a perfect alternative option to a condominium. Included is off street and covered parking--a rare find indeed. Walk from home to all your favorite activities; restaurants, coffee shops and bakeries, as all are close by.

Welcome to Crossridge Urban Community where modern sophistication meets neighborhood tradition! Brand new single family homes that have been thoughtfully designed with architectural & community integrity, each home feels custom with its elevated finishes and interior design. The Galbraith model features primary ensuite and all the living spaces on the main floor that extends out through modern French doors onto a large covered patio. Private backyard with 6' fence, gate, modern pavers, low maint turf and raised bed planters. Upstairs you'll find 2 more bedrooms with an additional full bath and large bonus room.

Welcome to your new home! This spacious home features 4 beds, 2.5 baths, with a large bonus room. Built with attention to detail and high-end finishes incl. quartz countertops throughout, undermount sinks, stainless steel appliances, hardwood engineered floors, custom upgraded tile work and hardware, shiplap accent ceiling, air conditioning and patio door with built in blinds. Covered extended patio, firepit and landscaping. It offers endless possibilities for relaxation and entertaining. Conveniently located near shops, schools, and parks. Don't miss your chance to make it your forever home.

Discover the irresistible charm of this contemporary NW home offering 4 BR/2.5BA & a versatile bonus room. The main level reveals a stunning primary suite w/ soaking tub, spacious separate shower, dbl vanity & walk-in closet. 3 more BR's on main offer flexible usage, w/ one ideal for an office. Enjoy quartz countertops, undermount sinks, SS appliances, gleaming hrdwd floors & upgraded tile & lighting. The heart of the home features a cozy gas FP in the open great room, providing a seamless flow to the covered deck back deck. This property sits on a generous .24-acre fenced corner lot. Spacious two-car garage, meticulously maintained landscaping & high-efficiency gas heating w/ central AC, ensuring year-round comfort & energy efficiency.

Discover the perfect opportunity with these two beautiful parcels, totaling 1.78 acres in the desirable Meridian school district. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, these are the last vacant lots off of Celtic Lane. The lots offer level, mostly cleared ground, a shop, and partial fencing, along with charming fruit trees. Enjoy the convenience of being just a short drive from shopping, downtown Bellingham, and only 20 minutes from the Canadian border. Store materials in the shop while you build on both lots or keep one for extra room to roam, this is an ideal setting for your dream home or investment.

Discover beach living in highly coveted Birch Bay Village! Breathtaking mountain, bay, city, & lake views. Refined luxury throughout this 4+bed/3 bath home w/main floor Primary, Utility & Den. Lower level w/3 guest rooms+ media/flex plumbed for wet bar, hidden wine cellar, library/game room-possibilities endless! Thoughtful details include doggie wash, heated 3 car garage, A/C, generator, recessed cove lighting, gourmet kit w/slab granite & stainless. Expansive trex deck w/access stairs on each end for great entertaining while enjoying the stunning panorama + trailer/RV parking. Unrivaled amenities: private marina, golf, beaches, clubhouse, pickleball/tennis, clubhouse, pool and more! Less than 2 hours from Seattle/15 min to the border!

Find beauty & tranquility in this updated Glenhaven rambler! Step inside the warm & inviting space to all new vinyl plank flooring, carpet, paint & lighting. Enjoy the updated kitchen w/ new quartz counters & appliances where sliding glass doors lead to a newer back deck- a perfect spot for morning coffee. A spacious ensuite primary bedrm, along w/ 2 other bedrms, laundry area and main bath makes for perfect one-floor living! Newer H2O heater, furnace, central air & ducting ensure year round efficiency. A separate adjacent lot is included & offers many possibilities! Attached oversized garage w/ ample storage. This delightful home promises comfort, modern convenience and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this haven your own!

Welcome home to this centrally located gem in Bellingham! Not only is this home nestled in a beautiful neighborhood in a cul-de-sac, it also offers a 2 car garage and a nearly 1/4 acre lot backing up to gorgeous trees and land with serene views. Situated just minutes from I-5, Costco, shopping centers, restaurants, parks, schools, and more, this charming 1305 sq ft rambler offers convenient and easy living. You'll love the cozy living room with wood fireplace, dining room and 3 cute bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This home is ready for your personal touch and updates. You can move in with peace of mind knowing that the home features a brand new roof, gutters, and fresh paint inside and out. Don't miss out on this fantastic home!

Views! Views! Views! Perched atop the gently rolling hill of Birch Bay, WA, this property boasts an unimpeded view that will take your breath away. Gaze out over the Strait of Georgia and the tranquil silhouette of Vancouver Island providing a picturesque backdrop against the setting sun, casting hues of orange and pink across the expanse of the bay. With every passing moment, the view from this vantage point is a mesmerizing symphony of color and light, offering a sense of serenity and wonder that is truly unparalleled. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a peaceful evening, truly breathless. Basement was being used as library. Home is a FIXER UPPER and needs lots of work.

Triplex Priced to Sell, AS IS! All 3 units feature 858 sq ft, 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, Generous sized Kitchen, Dining & Living Room. Unit C, top floor, is now purposely Vacant for ease of showing! It offers a sliding glass door to a large deck off the Living Room. Unit A is now vacant. New flooring just installed in A & C and units painted. All Units have the same floorplan with only the entry door being located in different spots in the Living Rooms. A & B are main floor units. Each Unit has a deck & share a large, fenced yard. Parking is in the Alley behind the home and there are 5 spaces. Each home has a separate, locking storage unit & there is a locking laundry room with coin operated washer/dryer for tenant use.

Welcome to Apres Lodge, a tastefully updated home in the popular Snowline community of Glacier. Located on a sunny lot with easy access to community amenities. This home lives big with a large loft on the second floor - use this space as a third bedroom & half bath or an extra flex space for rec room or office. Enjoy the well-designed kitchen with quartz countertops, providing lots of counterspace, & new appliances. The main floor hosts two bedrooms & a full bathroom with ample storage. Outside take advantage of the community pool, courts & playground or spend your days at Mt. Baker. Upon returning home you can unwind on the low maintenance composite deck, dine at your bistro table, warm up by the fire or hop in the large hot tub.

Sought after 4 bedroom Craftsman charmer in popular Bay Crest neighborhood that backs to a greenbelt...welcome to Clamdigger Drive! In the last 3 years: new roof, exterior paint, furnace + A/C, stainless steel kitchen appliances, LVP flooring and carpet. Flexible floor plan with main floor bedroom provides a great opportunity for a home office or private space tucked away from the other 3 bedrooms. Fenced backyard + attached 2 car garage. Quick and easy access to I-5 or leisurely stroll to the beach, there's never been a better time to live, love and enjoy all that Birch Bay has to offer. Stick built houses in this price range are rapidly disappearing...don't miss this one!

Discover your cozy sanctuary in the heart of Sudden Valley, WA. This delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bath home offers comfort and tranquility amidst nature's beauty with large windows and 3 skylights that flood the home with natural lights Benefit from the convenience of a standing crawl space, ideal for storing seasonal items and more.all while Embracing the outdoors on your own 0.33-acre lot, complete with a shed for additional storage or hobbies. Community Amenities: including parks, trails, and community activities, just moments away.

Welcome to your dream home! Nestled on a shy 2 acres, this 3-bedroom (potentially 4th), 3-bath beauty boasts Mt. Baker views, a spacious deck, and a cozy wood-burning stove. Light, bright, and great privacy throughout, this home has been tastefully updated over time. With a 2-car garage, detached shop, lush landscaping, fruit trees, garden space, and a greenhouse, it's an oasis of serenity. Set well off the road, the potential for subdivision and development makes it a rare find. Your perfect lifestyle awaits!

Large .42-acre view lot in sought after Boundary View Estates. Enjoy the quiet Pt Roberts lifestyle, only 45 minutes to Vancouver/30 minutes to YVR. Walk to beautiful Maple Beach on a path at the back of the lot in under 5 minutes. Deeded access to trail, waterfront, seashore and tidelands. A noted architect has created a visionary design fully utilizing the bay and mountain view potential. Features a huge great room with vaulted ceilings, and a secluded bedroom pavilion. Includes concept drawings, 3D architectural scale model, detailed topographic map. Ready-to-build - septic installed, lot cleared, community utilities underground. $900/yr HOA fees include lot mowing. Low 4.9% 15-yr owner financing w/25% down.

Enchanting acreage property just outside the city. This charming 2696 Sq ft abode features an open living space w/ high ceilings & abundant natural light. The kitchen beholds stainless steel appliances, ample counter space & storage. Cozy up to wood fireplace whilst sipping tea & pondering the meaning of life. The primary bed offers bath w/ tub and access to covered deck. 2 additional bedrooms + big bonus room upstairs makes expanding your brood a no-brainer. Uncle Jimbo needs a place to stay? We got you! This home has a sizable basement MIL suite with a kitchenette, rooms + separate W/D. Outside, you'll find a huge deck, room for a garden, 2 shops all on private, wooded 5 acres that screams do whatever you want. Priced to sell!

Welcome to this stunning and completely renovated home. This meticulously updated 3 bed, 2 bath house boasts a spacious 1550 square feet of living space. Step into the brand-new kitchen featuring sleek stainless steel appliances and modern finishes. Enjoy the luxury of all new flooring, heating, and a roof that will provide years of worry-free living. Indulge in the updated high-end primary bathroom for your private oasis. Don't miss out on this exceptional property that combines quality craftsmanship with modern amenities in a prime location-minutes from the beach, restaurants, and the Canadian border.

Fully remodeled rambler style home w/3 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms. This difficult-to-find gem has a shy 12, 000+ sq ft corner lot, is fully fenced, has a garage w/storage + carport, an outbuilding, fruit trees, garden space, a covered entrance, and a covered patio that will be enjoyed for years to come. Inside, you'll find a 20x23 great room to cozy up in front of a wood burning fireplace and brand-new kitchen & appliances. The primary suite has 2 separate closets & full bathroom, plus new carpets in all bedrooms. One year ago, the home's extensive renovation included a new roof, new insulation in the attic and crawl space, new floors, carpets, bathroom features, and new paint inside and out! This move-in-ready home is just waiting for you!

Welcome to St. Andrews Cottages in Semiahmoo! This 1, 800 sqft single story town-home offers easy living with lovely, sunny exposure. Wrap around deck showcases this spectacular location on the 14th fairway. Kitchen with eat-in space offers custom-furniture-grade cherry cabinets, tile back splash, and slab granite. Great room with fireplace & vaulted ceiling is open to the formal dining room. You'll love the award winning floor plan with excellent deck/patio access from great room, dining & kitchen. Two car garage offers lots of storage. Excellent use of space & well run Association makes this a great buy! Easy access to all that Semiahmoo has to offer--miles of walking/biking trails, resort amenities, world class golf & marine activities.

Whatcom Counties Premier Private Condo Storage facility with non-commercial use precluding outside traffic & securely gated & 24/7. This unit is 30x50 and uniquely equipped with Electric 14' Overhead Door, Gas Heat, Wall mounted Shop Vac, Shower, Larger Hot Water tank, terrific 14'x20' Mezzanine with wide staircase, Epoxy Floor. Room for 4+ cars or car boat combo. Conveniently located minutes from I-5. Pioneer Storage is Professionally managed and a beautifully maintained complex. HOA includes water common area maintenance etc. Extra wide aisles accommodate maneuvering large boats and RV's with ease. Why rent when you can own this consistently appreciating Real Estate investment. Hobbies, Collections, storage... you name it! as you own it.

Welcome to River-Walk, a unique 74-unit Northwest Washington community offering attractive design, luxurious finishes, beautiful views & pedestrian-friendly connectivity to Lynden. Walk or bike a few blocks to downtown to Lyndens quaint restaurants & stores. River-Walk is less than two hours to Seattle, Vancouver, B.C., Mt. Baker & the San Juan Islands. Lot 18 is in River-Walks west side, reserved for 55-and-older active adults with tech features including high-speed fiber optic cable. It offers a comfortable 1, 969 sq ft with 3 bedrooms & 2.25 bathrooms. The gourmet kitchen is highlighted by quartz countertops & islands with full waterfall drops. Reserve your new home now! Direct GPS to 202 Riverview Road, Lynden.

Open-concept living w/hardwood floors, lovely cherrywood cabinets, high ceilings & abundance of natural light. Dining room opens to a lg private deck, overlooking greenbelt. Family room is light-filled with large windows & high ceiling. A gas fireplace, with carved wood mantel adds warmth. Custom fir trim and railings add texture. Upstairs, the spacious Primary bdrm. features an ensuite, double closets & a view of lush cedar & maple trees. Second & 3rd Bdrms are nice sized, & share a full bath, w/ tub & shower. Two car attached garage w/storage. Very convenient southside location, situated on a quiet street, minutes to shopping & amenities. Energy efficient with gas furnace, gas hot water and high insulation values in walls and ceilings.

This single-story condo features a wall of windows facing the backyard offering a partial Lake Whatcom view. Vaulted ceilings throughout with clerestory windows create a very open & bright feeling throughout. Updated LVP flooring throughout the main living areas. Enjoy the comfort of a gas freestanding fireplace, the privacy of the front porch & the convenience of the 1-car garage. Third bedroom was converted into living space - it could be walled off again if additional sleeping space is desired. Located in a very walkable part of Sudden Valley where you can easily access swimming pools, tennis courts, lakefront beaches, a community center, restaurants, WTA bus route 512 & more!

Escape the hustle and bustle of the city, and come enjoy this 4.72 acre property with an adorable rambler, barn, shed, and is nestled at the base of the Sumas Mountains! The 2 bedroom home boasts an open concept floorplan, updated flooring, gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a cozy wood stove. Outside is your personal oasis - established garden beds, ample room for outdoor hobbies & activities, dog run, fencing around the perimeter, mature landscaping, and plenty of pasture space. Set in a serene and private location, with easy access to commuter routes, and more! Don't miss out on this chance to make this hobby farm your own slice of paradise.

Birch Bay life all year! Superbly remodeled/landscaped, feels new manu home in Edgewater Resort - 576 SF, 2BR, 1 full BA. Park directly across street from beach w/unforgettable sunsets. New electrical panel & system installed 2023. Grass field in front for recreation w/no plans for development. Interior of home has been stylishly updated-windows, LVP floors, paint, cabinets, tiling, lighting, hot water tank, more. Large covered deck on side for year 'round outdoor living. Gas BBQs allowed. Lots of room on sides. Greenbelt in back & patio w/new shed. No short term rentals. Stacking washer/dryer hookups in home. New TPO roof 2019. Sprinklers on timer, WIFI thermostat, security system. This is the downsized Birch Bay life at the beach!

Calling all first-time buyers and investors! Fantastic condo conveniently located in the heart of Bellingham! You will feel right at home in this spacious 2 bed, 1.5 bath condo. Laminate flooring throughout the main floor, and new carpet installed on the second floor and stairs. Updated kitchen boasts granite countertops and stainless appliances. French doors off the dining area lead to your private covered patio for year-round enjoyment. Upstairs, you will find a very spacious primary bedroom with ample storage, along with a second bedroom and a full bathroom in the hall. Bikeable location, and within 5-10 minutes drive to Costco and most parts of town. New elementary school and park across the street. Dues cover W/S/G. NO RENTAL CAP.

Welcome to this beautifully renovated 4 bedroom 2 bath home out in the county, well situated off the road, with a gentle creek lining the property and a private campground out back. Just outside of Bellingham, Lynden, and Everson. New roof, flooring, master bath, kitchen with quartz countertops and new LG stainless steel appliances. So many possibilities on a 15 acre lot with 2 separate electric meters. One for the home and one for your future shop and RV. Plenty of space for your livestock and crops! NOT IN THE FLOOD PLAIN.

Presale. Make your color and upgrade selections. Salt water & sea breezes greet you! Cypress, offered in the new gated community Woodberry, at Semiahmoo. 2690 sq ft. The main level lives like a one level home with Primary, office, dining room, open floor plan, kitchen and living with 1.5 baths, enjoy 2 bedrooms, bath and loft area upstairs. Quality finishes, flooring, quartz, soft close cabinets, stainless appliances, mini split heating / Quality limited life time roof, patio & more. 25 minutes from Costco. 10 minutes from border. Area amenities are ala carte and include Golf & CC, Marina, waterfront park, 200 room Inn at Semiahmoo, Spa, Tennis club, walking trails kayaking, biking. 2 Car gar. Brokers registration policy #4908.

Welcome to River-Walk, a unique NW Washington community offering attractive design, luxurious finishes, beautiful views and pedestrian-friendly connectivity to Lynden, a safe and well-maintained city of 16, 000. Residents can walk or bike a few blocks to downtown Lyndens quaint restaurants and stores, plus theyre less than two hours to Seattle, Vancouver, B.C., Mt. Baker and the San Juan Islands. Lot 42 is on River-Walks east side. It offers a comfortable 1423 sq. ft. with 2 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms and many upgrades. The gourmet kitchen is highlighted by quartz countertops and islands with full waterfall drops. Direct GPS to 202 Riverview Road, Lynden.

Nestled on a sunny corner lot, this charming 4-bed/1.75-bath farmhouse is waiting for you! The main floor features 2 beds + 3/4 bath and flows seamlessly from the living room through the large dining room, and into the updated kitchen with SS appliances, granite countertops, and lots of cabinet space. Upstairs you'll find an expansive primary bedroom, full bath, guest bedroom, and bonus area. The bevy of windows keep the home awash in natural light while the fully fenced backyard offers privacy. 50-year metal roof, covered front porch, and parking in the back. Just minutes from the harbor, I-5, the border, and downtown Blaine. Come see it while you can!

Light and bright, top floor end unit! Welcome home to your airy 2 bedroom condo in the heart of Lynden. With windows on three sides of the unit and vaulted ceiling in the living room, you will always enjoy the natural light and fresh breeze even on those grey PNW days. Built in 2020, this unit still feels fresh and new with quartz countertops, stainless appliances, and new washer/dryer in 2023. Relax on your private balcony, overlooking a tranquil green space with a creek down below, and the mountains in the distance. Ideal location close to restaurants, shopping, and easy access to the Guide Meridian and Canadian border. Low HOA dues cover central hot water, W/S/G, grounds maintenance. Designated covered parking space + storage unit.

Fantastic 2 story home in the King Mountain Community with seasonal Bellingham Bay views, located on a corner lot. Low maintenance fenced back yard and covered back deck for enjoying the outdoor life year around. Only a few minutes from shopping, restaurants, and all the great things Bellingham has to offer! High end finishes throughout. Soft close cabinets, engineered wood, gas fireplace in the living room with a stone surround, and a wonderfully western exposure for amazing sunsets! Three bedrooms with laundry located on the same level as all bedrooms for convenience and a level driveway! You're going to love it!

Rare opportunity to build your custom dream home on charming Lynn Street in the heart of the Columbia neighborhood! Close to Columbia Elementary, parks, and restaurants. Building plans available for a 1850sqft, 3 bed, 2.5 bath home. City-approved for main house with 2 ADUs. Previous home was demolished, lot is leveled and cleared with water on site and sewer/power in alley. Water/sewer/transp/school impact fees credited with the city saving over $25k. Bring your vision and start building your NEW home today!

One-level living (level entry) on this level lot on a corner alleyway Bellingham home. Well-designed floorplan. 9-foot high ceilings. Home is near Samish /WWU I5 exit but w/o the noise. Has private feel to neighborhood due to being on dead-end street. A great equation of features make this a home ready for your updates! Built 1998. 3 BRs, 2 full BAs. 1, 520 SF. Fenced backyard. Primary BR is spacious & has primary full bathroom-2 sinks and separate closet. Skylight, natural gas fireplace in living room. Cement planked siding. South facing.
